data.description: Pack up your family and all your animals with this wonderfully set up home, INSIDE and OUTSIDE to accommodate horses, goats, chickens, pigs, whatever your heart desires!  The owners added in 2021 a shed row barn with 3 12x12 matted stalls, added a 65x135 outdoor sand arena, added a 2 acre split pasture (1 acre each with gate between) with electro braid fencing and made the driveway much larger in the back for easy turn-around.  There is a chicken coop (currently used for goats) with electricity in it.  Inside there is so much character and charm with all the beautiful woodwork, crown molding and solid wood doors and high ceilings. Nicely remodeled Large Kitchen with many cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Both bathrooms have been updated.  Newer electric box, HWT 13 yrs old, furnace roughly 13 yrs old. Great front porch to enjoy with a porch swing out front and newer patio (2022) in the back between house and garage. Lots of space to run around on this 5.2 acre lot!  (Dining room has a closet if you wanted to make it a first floor bedroom)
